title: Captain's Paradise (1953) Alec Guiness Yvonne de Carlo
description:
Much imitated comedy about a ferry captain (Alec Guinness) with a wife in each port. The wife in Gibraltar is solid and dependable, the one in Spanish Morocco is sexy and enticing. Naturally there are surprise twists...

This is a ROTTEN copy, ripped from a very old tape - at least I have been able to beef up the volume. I will take this down if someone posts a better one.
